cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.IR 

This paper deals with biomedical image analysis algorithms and proposes a set of methods to analyze and visualize the results of challenges. The paper also introduces an open-source framework for the same. The most relevant sub-category for this paper is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition), followed by cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.MM (Multimedia), and cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
